text="Existence of Algebraic Closures">Existence of Algebraic Closures</fr:title><fr:taxon>Proposition</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2025</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>21</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
